Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st1902 Description

ST 1902 Motion Imagery Metadata (MIMD): Model-to-KLV Transmutation Instructions.

ST 1901, ST 1902, ST 1903, ST 1904, ST 1905, ST 1906, ST 1907 and ST 1908 collectively define Motion Imagery Metadata (MIMD).

ST 1902 This standard defines the Model-to-KLVTransmutation Instructions for constructing bandwidth efficient KLV structures from the model. Other formats such as XML or JSON may have transmutation instructions developed for them in future revisions.
